Evicted Big Brother Naija housemate, Esther has revealed the likely winner of ‘Pepper Dem’ edition. Esther who was evicted on Sunday during the BBNaija live eviction show said either Sir Dee or Frodd will be the winner. She said this while having a chat with Ebuka Obi-Uchendu on stage after her eviction from the house. Esther said: “I think Frodd or Sir Dee will be the winner.” Meanwhile, 13 housemates are left in the BBNaija house to compete for the grand prize of N60m. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.